{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"18519-lost-and-found","title":"Gesucht und gefunden","description":"Ein kleiner Junge sucht nach etwas, das er verloren hat. Rate mal, was passiert, als er es wieder findet. Lies weiter, um es herauszufinden!","language":"German","langCode":"de","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Gaby Triess"],"illustrators":["Sukhada Rahalkar"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/18519-lost-and-found"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/709189/size3/097ef1a9bc1497c04e9ec0987d19adac.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/709189/size6/097ef1a9bc1497c04e9ec0987d19adac.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4355/size6/71b081c372839a4e1e1832d121aac93b.jpg","text":"Nicht hier und nicht dort.\nWo bist Du? An welchem Ort?","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4356/size6/2229e96f2fb720ac002e3c8f62f0b655.jpg","text":"Nicht unter'm Sofa.\nNicht unter'm Bettchen.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4357/size6/226e15b7017b30e23c3c382790b6b683.jpg","text":"Nicht in der Kiste.\nNicht unter'm Röckchen meiner Schwester.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4358/size6/1364e4a6391bdb15c1be7aa264b31951.jpg","text":"Nicht unter'm Kissen.\nNicht in der Tasche.\nBuuhuu, wo bist Du hin?","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4359/size6/fec3256b52d1d0ab91ad2bdddced791a.jpg","text":"Ich hab in jedem Zimmer nachgeschaut.\nIch hab unter jedes Buch gekuckt.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4360/size6/dbef9cebc51fe64c9fb9301cf170928d.jpg","text":"Ich hab unter'm Sessel nachgesehen.\nIch hab unter'm Stuhl gekuckt.\nWo bist Du nur hin?","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4361/size6/8db6b1bf9853fe293b13b72a50d6f1de.jpg","text":"Kurz darauf kam die Oma vom Spatzierengehen zurück.\n„Schau, was ich im Park gefunden hab!“","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4362/size6/c0452bea31292c39aaf3a68b9e4c5c2b.jpg","text":"„Es schaukelt und hüpft,\nes dreht sich und baumelt,\nHaha, hihi\" kicherte die Oma.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4363/size6/0e2508ca2706df242be6399e32bf4078.jpg","text":"„Ach Omi! Vielen lieben Dank!\nDu hast mein Jo-Jo gefunden!\"","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4364/size6/145214864074aa8884d2a86d02eb8457.jpg","text":"„Jo-Jo? Was für ein lustiger Name!\nWas für ein lustiges Teil!\nDa spiel ich gleich damit,\ndas ist ja der Hit!\"","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4365/size6/dd29b24c1af5eb00337353345140bead.jpg","text":"Kicker, kicher, h¨örte ich sie heiter,\nmit meinem Jo-Jo spielte die Oma,\nden ganzen Tag weiter!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":141}}